    "Examples include technologies like humanID, OpenID, next-generation CAPTCHAs [27], etc.",
    "In GenAI:• Proof of Identity can ensure that AI-generated content or actions can be traced back to a legitimate source.",
    "• Methods might include multi-factor authentication, biometric verification, or digital certificates.Authentication protocols: Authentication protocols are processes or systems used to confirm the identity of an individual, system, or entity.",
